headlines.description: — Kevin Durant sat and smiled, trying to speak loudly enough to be heard in a jubilant locker room.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kevin Durant scores season-high 41 points, Suns snap 3-game skid with 120-106 win over Pistons

events.name: Toronto Raptors at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — The Toronto Raptors overcame a sizeable deficit and an even larger presence in San Antonio Spurs rookie sensation Victor Wembanyama to win for the first time on the road this season.
headlines.shortLinkText: Raptors overcome 22-point deficit, beat Spurs 123-116 in OT

events.name: Golden State Warriors at Cleveland Cavaliers

headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell had 31 points and seven assists and the Cleveland Cavaliers beat Golden State 115-104 on Sunday night, ending a 16-game losing streak against the Warriors.
headlines.shortLinkText: Donovan Mitchell scores 31 points, Cavaliers beat Warriors to end 16-game series skid

headlines.description: — Luka Doncic didn't have quite the fourth quarter that LaMelo Ball had.
headlines.shortLinkText: Luka Doncic, Mavs overcome LaMelo Ball's 30-point triple-double in 124-118 win over Hornets

events.name: Memphis Grizzlies at Portland Trail Blazers

headlines.description: — The Memphis Grizzlies knew that a win would eventually come, sooner rather than later.
headlines.shortLinkText: Memphis beats Portland 112-100 for first win of the season
